name: Get Empty Rack
query: SELECT rack_no FROM location_rack where id_pallet is null order by rack_no limit 1;

name: Record Data
query: UPDATE location_rack set id_pallet={{msg.id_pallet}}, storage_time = now() where rack_no={{msg.payload}};

name: Empty All Rack
query: UPDATE location_rack set id_pallet = null, storage_time = null;

name: Get Pallet in Rack
query:
SELECT distinct a.id_pallet,name FROM location_rack a inner join master_material b on a.id_pallet = b.id_pallet 
where a.id_pallet is not null order by id_pallet;

Get Table Location
query:
SELECT a.rack_no, a.id_pallet,TO_CHAR(a.storage_time,'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:ss') as storage_time,b.name,b.value 
FROM location_rack a 
inner join master_material b on a.id_pallet=b.id_pallet
order by a.rack_no ;

name: Get Table Location
query:
SELECT * FROM location_rack
order by rack_no ;

Get Total
query:
SELECT count(rack_no) as total_loc FROM location_rack
Where id_pallet is not null

name: Get Total
query:
select a.id_pallet,b."name",sum(b.value) as total from location_rack a 
inner join master_material b on a.id_pallet=b.id_pallet 
where a.id_pallet is not null
group by a.id_pallet,b."name" order by total desc
